# Reflaxe.Elixir Test Runner Configuration
# Based on Reflaxe.CPP and Reflaxe.CSharp testing patterns
#
# Usage:
#   haxe test/Test.hxml                    # Run all tests
#   haxe test/Test.hxml test=liveview      # Run specific test
#   haxe test/Test.hxml update-intended    # Update expected output
#   haxe test/Test.hxml help               # Show help

-cp test
--run test.TestRunner